# Stage 11 — Multi-Pipeline System + UI Config

> **Prerequisite:** Stage 10 must be complete with test_stage10.py passing 100%.

## Goal
Make the Lineage Engine work with **multiple pipelines** (not just Jaffle Shop). Developers can add a new pipeline by dropping a single file into `pipelines/`. Users can switch the active pipeline from both the **CLI** and the **browser UI**. The frontend also gets a config panel for changing the **API URL** (for connecting to different backend instances).

---

